prompt: An ancient tree in an enchanted forest, anime style, glowing symbols carved into the trunk, surrounded by magical energy. The scene should be mystical and awe-inspiring.
revised_prompt: An ancient tree stands as the heart of an enchanted forest. The rounded, gnarled roots rise from the forest floor, leading your eyes up to the thick, expansive trunk. Carved into the bark are symbols, glowing with luminescent energy, their radiance contrasted by the rough texture of the tree bark. This mysterious tree is encapsulated within a swirling whirl of magical energy, illuminating the dark forest around it in a dazzling array of colors. The overall scene is one of mysticism and awe, prompting a sense of wonderment in anyone fortunate to behold such a sight.
